{"type":"message","id":"e46df212","parentId":"90b6a254","timestamp":"2026-03-22T11:35:36.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"扒一下\"，应该是想让我查看某个笔记的详细内容。让我看看刚才列表中最热门的是哪些，选一个来获取详情。\n\n最热门的几个：\n- 成都一些不会踩雷的店 (点赞2825, 收藏3770) - id: 666d31950000000006006200\n- 好吃到烫嘴 (点赞4.6万) - id: 699862040000000016009a3f\n- 成都必吃6家平价米其林川菜馆 - id: 692d1b0f000000001e003247\n\n让我查一下\"成都一些不会踩雷的店\"这个笔记的详情。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ayf3euxvobhn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call xiaohongshu get_feed_detail feed_id=666d31950000000006006200 xsec_token=ABRCtICrer_wYQHAuUTUKG8HFdIoED_lggOAGIlI5Ar3s","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774179322262}}
{"type":"message","id":"71c9957e","parentId":"e46df212","timestamp":"2026-03-22T11:35:45.575Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ayf3euxvobhn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"feed_id\": \"666d31950000000006006200\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"note\": {\n      \"noteId\": \"666d31950000000006006200\",\n      \"xsecToken\": \"ABRCtICrer_wYQHAuUTUKG8HFdIoED_lggOAGIlI5Ar3s\",\n      \"title\": \"成都一些不会踩雷的店\",\n      \"desc\": \"以下都是土生土长三十多年吃过无脑推的店\\n西餐-the river house\\n川菜-许家菜（望江店）、芙蓉凰、屋顶上的樱园\\n特色川菜-漫得食堂\\n福建菜-宴遇\\n苏浙淮阳菜-新荣记、游园京梦\\n意大利菜-末本\\n粤菜-麓轩、丁海记\\n法甜-福洛小面包\\n提拉米苏-凉浸浸（只要能订得上，无脑冲）、bake no title、jojonana\\n苹果肉桂-bake no title\\n糖水-凉浸浸，依旧小屋\\n点心-slow&taste、kez's coffee的下午茶（点香蕉太妃派和英式松饼就好，其他太太太甜了）\\n咖啡-福满咖啡（玉林）\\n提拉米苏/brunch -cafe de coucou\\n苹果派及杏仁巧克力可颂-热晨烘焙\\n小面-合盛小面（金沙店）\\n烧椒拌鸡面-魏四爷面馆（金房店）\\n没有网红店\\n无利益相关\\n实实在在硬货餐厅\\n[微笑R][微笑R][微笑R]\\n#川菜[话题]# #我的宝藏美食集[话题]# #吃吃喝喝[话题]# #周末吃什么[话题]# #唯有美食可以治愈一切[话题]# #\",\n      \"type\": \"normal\",\n      \"time\": 1718432149000,\n      \"ipLocation\": \"\",\n      \"user\": {\n        \"userId\": \"5e41766300000000010032b6\",\n        \"nickname\": \"yiyi\",\n        \"nickName\": \"\",\n        \"avatar\": \"https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo314aimjh9mg6g5ni1ephg8clmobpovso\"\n      },\n      \"interactInfo\": {\n        \"liked\": false,\n        \"likedCount\": \"2825\",\n        \"sharedCount\": \"\",\n        \"commentCount\": \"142\",\n        \"collectedCount\": \"3770\",\n        \"collected\": false\n      },\n      \"imageList\": [\n        {\n          \"width\": 2560,\n          \"height\": 1920,\n          \"urlDefault\": \"http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221935/10887b80db1f77f89de5e95ae280b754/1040g0083142ahg8vhm605ni1ephg8clmn4t8ho0!nd_dft_wgth_webp_3\",\n          \"urlPre\": \"http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221935/783d53c99261d0148db17f1b48db55d2/1040g0083142ahg8vhm605ni1ephg8clmn4t8ho0!nd_prv_wgth_webp_3\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"comments\": {\n      \"list\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"666eb1c9000000002100f538\",\n          \"noteId\": \"666d31950000000006006200\",\n          \"content\": \"river house 真没毛病\",\n          \"likeCount\": \"27\",\n          \"createTime\": 1718530505000,\n          \"ipLocation\": \"\",\n          \"liked\": false,\n          \"userInfo\": {\n            \"userId\": \"5eba79700000000001005dbd\",\n            \"nickname\": \"用户已注销\",\n            \"nickName\": \"\",\n            \"avatar\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"subCommentCount\": \"12\",\n          \"subComments\": [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"666ed0f3000000002100cb81\",\n              \"noteId\": \"666d31950000000006006200\",\n              \"content\": \"是啊，菜品服务十多年都品质在线。同价位天花板了\",\n              \"likeCount\": \"10\",\n              \"createTime\": 1718538483000,\n              \"ipLocation\": \"\",\n              \"liked\": false,\n              \"userInfo\": {\n                \"userId\": \"5e41766300000000010032b6\",\n                \"nickname\": \"yiyi\",\n                \"nickName\": \"\",\n                \"avatar\": \"\"\n              },\n              \"subCommentCount\": \"\",\n              \"subComments\": null,\n              \"showTags\": [\n                \"is_author\"\n              ]\n            }\n          ],\n          \"showTags\": []\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"666da913000000002101ed92\",\n          \"noteId\": \"666d31950000000006006200\",\n          \"content\": \"有无平价版推荐，穷人一个[扯脸H][扯脸H][扯脸H]\",\n          \"likeCount\": \"9\",\n          \"createTime\": 1718462739000,\n          \"ipLocation\": \"\",\n          \"liked\": false,\n          \"userInfo\": {\n            \"userId\": \"5b749011ad4ba90001717723\",\n            \"nickname\": \"Wwwww\",\n            \"nickName\": \"\",\n            \"avatar\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"subCommentCount\": \"29\",\n          \"subComments\": [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"666ec5