{"type":"message","id":"ed4f64cc","parentId":"fe0c969c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T11:46:33.872Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mhbxow0iy1b5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"feed_id\": \"63d8d611000000001d01cdf8\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"note\": {\n      \"noteId\": \"63d8d611000000001d01cdf8\",\n      \"xsecToken\": \"ABzRROaayhVlIjYbV-sOz-Iabirh6lG8fKcK37ipG2gns\",\n      \"title\": \"成都📍人均50家庭聚餐 老爸直夸我选得好！\",\n      \"desc\": \"这次家庭聚餐地方是我选择的！由于家里有老人小孩，特意挑了一家老牌川菜馆，符合所有的胃口🤩\\n·\\n来之前特意看了下评价，他家大多数都是成都本地回头客，满满一桌吃下来，人均50r差不多，好吃不贵👏🏻\\n·\\n✔️鲜椒烧牛掌\\n好辣好辣！满嘴的胶原蛋白！口感hin耙糯，吃到最后发现还有泡面！十分入味弹牙！\\n·\\n✔️醋香小煎鸡\\n他家卖了几万份的招牌菜之一，鸡块吃起来hin香！外酥里嫩。\\n·\\n✔️香菜牛肉丝\\n干饭神器！！香菜爱好者一定要点！牛肉丝ju丝滑～又香又嫩！\\n铁盒蛋炒饭也巴适！满满的童年回忆！粒粒分明，里面还加了辣椒的！\\n·\\n🔺这家店装修宽敞明亮，我们选择的是可容纳十余人的包间。\\n#成都旅游[话题]# #成都美食[话题]# #成都川菜[话题]# #成都必吃[话题]#\",\n      \"type\": \"normal\",\n      \"time\": 1675154961000,\n      \"ipLocation\": \"\",\n      \"user\": {\n        \"userId\": \"554ad60bb203d9582645329f\",\n        \"nickname\": \"肉球球大白\",\n        \"nickName\": \"\",\n        \"avatar\": \"https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/1040g2jo31tk3b3g8ne0040icrfb0mckvlkb9kfo\"\n      },\n      \"interactInfo\": {\n        \"liked\": false,\n        \"likedCount\": \"356\",\n        \"sharedCount\": \"\",\n        \"commentCount\": \"43\",\n        \"collectedCount\": \"299\",\n        \"collected\": false\n      },\n      \"imageList\": [\n        {\n          \"width\": 1440,\n          \"height\": 1920,\n          \"urlDefault\": \"http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221946/543949a859f211f385923bf114440a2b/1000g0081vlpdc80eu00040icrfb0mckvgl2s3bo!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3\",\n          \"urlPre\": \"http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221946/fe6b614628eceb40983f7219a7127c91/1000g0081vlpdc80eu00040icrfb0mckvgl2s3bo!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"width\": 1440,\n          \"height\": 1920,\n          \"urlDefault\": \"http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/2026