{"type":"message","id":"794ada86","parentId":"22edf949","timestamp":"2026-03-22T11:47:00.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"获取到了两家餐厅的图片！让我给用户描述一下环境。"},{"type":"text","text":"两家餐厅的环境图都有了！\n\n## 1. 蜀上肴（科华店）- 人均50\n\n🏠 **环境**：装修宽敞明亮，普通川菜馆风格，有包间\n\n![图1](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221946/543949a859f211f385923bf114440a2b/1000g0081vlpdc80eu00040icrfb0mckvgl2s3bo!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3)\n\n![图2](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221946/2c890811d6f81549c2a7408b2fdc0df1/1000g0081vlpdc80eu00g40icrfb0mckvv16nj48!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3)\n\n---\n\n## 2. 大厨小味 - 人均60\n\n🏠 **环境**：独栋小楼，青砖木门，老成都院子风格，一楼大堂敞亮，四楼有包间+机麻房\n\n![图1](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221946/5d3d4dc9fd79db214ca210fff21f67e6/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831hvlnkqc6d3049gvg7nicebrhc5cmbg!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3)\n\n![图2](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202603221946/0f133451bef6dcef190876a877b786c6/notes_pre_post/1040g3k831hvlnkqc6d3g49gvg7nicebr4vkceo8!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3)\n\n---\n\n**对比：**\n| | 蜀上肴 | 大厨小味 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 人均 | 50 | 60 |\n| 环境 | 宽敞明亮 | 老成都院坝风格 |\n| 包间 | ✅ | ✅ + 机麻 |\n| 特色 | 本地回头客多 | 可以打麻将喝茶 |\n\n你选哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774180009253}}
